description: "Query: clickbench_q22"
---
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |   Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |   Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |     Projection: hits.SearchPhrase, min(hits.URL), count(Int64(1)) AS c                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |       Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.SearchPhrase]], aggr=[[min(hits.URL), count(Int64(1))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |         TableScan: hits projection=[URL, SearchPhrase], full_filters=[hits.URL LIKE Utf8("%google%"), hits.SearchPhrase != Utf8("")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |     VirtualExecutionPlan name=postgres compute_context=host=Tcp("benchmarking-postgres-rw.dataplatform.svc.cluster.local"),port=5432,db=clickbench_accelerated,user=postgres, initial_sql=SELECT "hits"."SearchPhrase", min("hits"."URL"), count(1) AS "c" FROM "hits" WHERE ("hits"."URL" LIKE '%google%' AND ("hits"."SearchPhrase" <> '')) GROUP BY "hits"."SearchPhrase" ORDER BY "c" DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
